# Build-time public env for the client bundle. Copy to `.env` (gitignored) and
# fill in real values. Only `PUBLIC_`-prefixed vars are exposed to the browser by
# Astro; server secrets belong in `.dev.vars` (see `.dev.vars.example`) instead.

# Stripe test-mode PUBLISHABLE key (issue #65). Safe in the browser by design —
# it only identifies the account to Stripe.js, it cannot move money. Used by
# src/components/CheckoutEmbed.tsx to load Stripe.js and mount the embedded
# Checkout. MUST be a test key (starts with `pk_test_`); pair it with the
# matching `sk_test_` secret in `.dev.vars`.
PUBLIC_STRIPE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY="pk_test_replace_me"
